                            <comment id="12986604" author="ciemo" created="Tue, 25 Jan 2011 18:56:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also, is an &quot;include&quot; mechanism supported so that we can have a &quot;library&quot; of JavaScript functions that we reuse from script to script?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
